stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> no_update
  no_update --> update_available: backend artifact prepared
  update_available --> checking_quiescence: detector poll
  checking_quiescence --> waiting_for_idle: active or pending chain exists
  waiting_for_idle --> checking_quiescence: job or follow-up state changes
  checking_quiescence --> auto_update_eligible: no active or pending chain
  auto_update_eligible --> updating: deterministic update starts
  updating --> post_validation: backend restarted
  post_validation --> updated_pending_ack: health and validation pass
  post_validation --> failed: validation fails
  updated_pending_ack --> acknowledged: user dismisses notice
  acknowledged --> no_update: notice cleared

  update_available --> force_requested: user confirms force
  waiting_for_idle --> force_requested: user confirms force
  force_requested --> updating: record interruptions

  failed --> waiting_for_idle: retry waits for idle
  failed --> force_requested: user confirms force retry

  note right of waiting_for_idle
    Not idle includes active CLI jobs,
    active_agent_run_id, queued or reserved
    agent turns, Generator -> Reviewer
    follow-ups, Summary follow-ups,
    SDD/Codex jobs, Project Factory jobs,
    and pending background tasks.
  end note
